{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852448912,"sessionID":"ses_286f27b45ffeMq6hIQGqkgco09","part":{"id":"prt_d790dec6a001PvzxrajqunaQ4y","messageID":"msg_d790dd6780014SNm2F2qrRR0HO","sessionID":"ses_286f27b45ffeMq6hIQGqkgco09","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c52f9f1dc7ec4779b9114422849cdde1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Router JWT 认证与签发 Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 实现 Router 模块的 JWT（JSON Web Token）认证与签发功能，为 AgentCube 平台提供安全的会话认证机制。该模块负责生成、验证和管理 JWT 令牌，用于认证和授权 Router 请求，确保只有合法的会话才能访问后端服务。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: JWT 令牌生成与会话关联\n10: \n11: The system SHALL generate a JWT token for each session using RS256 signing algorithm with the session ID included in the claims.\n12: \n13: #### Scenario: 生成包含会话 ID 的 JWT 令牌\n14: - **GIVEN** a valid session ID and initialized JWT manager with RSA key pair\n15: - **WHEN** GenerateToken is called with the session ID\n16: - **THEN** a JWT token is returned with session_id claim containing the provided session ID\n17: - **AND** the token includes standard RegisteredClaims with IssuedAt, ExpiresAt, and NotBefore timestamps\n18: - **AND** the token is signed using RS256 algorithm\n19: \n20: #### Scenario: 生成的令牌包含标准声明\n21: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized with private key\n22: - **WHEN** a token is generated\n23: - **THEN** the token contains IssuedAt set to current time\n24: - **AND** ExpiresAt is set to current time plus jwtTokenExpiration (5 minutes)\n25: - **AND** NotBefore is set to current time\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: 生成令牌失败当私钥未初始化\n28: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager without initialized private key\n29: - **WHEN** GenerateToken is called\n30: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating JWT manager not initialized with private key\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: JWT 令牌验证与签名检查\n33: \n34: The system SHALL validate JWT tokens by verifying the RSA signature and checking expiration time.\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: 验证有效的 JWT 令牌\n37: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT token generated by the system\n38: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n39: - **THEN** the JWT claims are successfully extracted\n40: - **AND** the session_id claim contains the original session ID\n41: - **AND** no error is returned\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: 验证过期令牌\n44: - **GIVEN** a JWT token that has expired (ExpiresAt is in the past)\n45: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n46: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token has expired\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: 验证无效签名的令牌\n49: - **GIVEN** a JWT token with tampered signature\n50: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n51: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token is invalid\n52: \n53: #### Scenario: 验证格式错误的令牌\n54: - **GIVEN** a malformed JWT token string\n55: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n56: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token format is invalid\n57: \n58: #### Scenario: 验证令牌失败当公钥未初始化\n59: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager without initialized public key\n60: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n61: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating JWT manager not initialized with public key\n62: \n63: ### Requirement: RSA 密钥对生成\n64: \n65: The system SHALL generate RSA 2048-bit key pairs for JWT signing and verification.\n66: \n67: #### Scenario: 生成 RSA 密钥对\n68: - **GIVEN** no existing RSA keys\n69: - **WHEN** generateRSAKeyPair is called\n70: - **THEN** an RSA private key with 2048 bits is returned\n71: - **AND** the corresponding public key is derived from the private key\n72: - **AND** no error is returned\n73: \n74: #### Scenario: 密钥对包含私钥和公钥\n75: - **GIVEN** a generated RSA key pair\n76: - **WHEN** the key pair is examined\n77: - **THEN** the private key can be used for signing\n78: - **AND** the public key can be used for verification\n79: - **AND** the public key matches the private key\n80: \n81: ### Requirement: 密钥持久化到 Kubernetes Secret\n82: \n83: The system SHALL store RSA keys in a Kubernetes Secret named \"agentcube-jwt-keys\" with private.pem and public.pem data fields.\n84: \n85: #### Scenario: 首次启动时创建密钥 Secret\n86: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster and no existing JWT key Secret\n87: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with a valid clientset and namespace\n88: - **THEN** a new Secret is created with name \"agentcube-jwt-keys\"\n89: - **AND** the Secret contains \"private.pem\" with PEM-encoded private key\n90: - **AND** the Secret contains \"public.pem\" with PEM-encoded public key\n91: - **AND** the Secret is created in the specified namespace\n92: \n93: #### Scenario: 从现有 Secret 加载密钥\n94: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster with an existing JWT key Secret\n95: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called\n96: - **THEN** the existing keys are loaded from the Secret\n97: - **AND** no new Secret is created\n98: - **AND** the keys match the values stored in the Secret\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: Secret 不存在时生成密钥并存储\n101: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster without the JWT key Secret\n102: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called\n103: - **THEN** new RSA keys are generated\n104: - **AND** the keys are stored in a new Secret\n105: - **AND** the JWT manager is initialized with the generated keys\n106: \n107: ### Requirement: 密钥加载和解析\n108: \n109: The system SHALL parse PEM-encoded RSA keys from Kubernetes Secret data.\n110: \n111: #### Scenario: 解析 PEM 编码的私钥\n112: - **GIVEN** a valid PEM-encoded RSA private key block with type \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"\n113: - **WHEN** parsePrivateKeyPEM is called with the PEM data\n114: - **THEN** an RSA private key is successfully parsed\n115: - **AND** no error is returned\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: 解析 PEM 编码的公钥\n118: - **GIVEN** a valid PEM-encoded RSA public key block with type \"PUBLIC KEY\"\n119: - **WHEN** parsePublicKeyPEM is called with the PEM data\n120: - **THEN** an RSA public key is successfully parsed\n121: - **AND** no error is returned\n122: \n123: #### Scenario: 解析无效的私钥格式\n124: - **GIVEN** an invalid PEM-encoded private key\n125: - **WHEN** parsePrivateKeyPEM is called\n126: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the PEM block is invalid\n127: \n128: #### Scenario: 解析无效的公钥格式\n129: - **GIVEN** an invalid PEM-encoded public key\n130: - **WHEN** parsePublicKeyPEM is called\n131: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the PEM block is invalid\n132: \n133: #### Scenario: Secret 缺少必需的密钥字段\n134: - **GIVEN** a Secret without \"private.pem\" or \"public.pem\" field\n135: - **WHEN** loadKeysFromSecret is called with the Secret\n136: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the missing field\n137: \n138: ### Requirement: JWT 管理器初始化\n139: \n140: The system SHALL initialize JWT manager with kubernetes clientset and optionally use default namespace when not specified.\n141: \n142: #### Scenario: 使用显式命名空间初始化\n143: - **GIVEN** a valid kubernetes clientset and a namespace string\n144: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with the clientset and namespace\n145: - **THEN** a JWT manager is returned with the configured namespace\n146: - **AND** the manager is initialized with keys from the Secret or newly generated\n147: \n148: #### Scenario: 使用默认命名空间初始化\n149: - **GIVEN** a valid kubernetes clientset and empty namespace string\n150: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with empty namespace\n151: - **THEN** a JWT manager is returned with default namespace (\"agentcube\")\n152: - **AND** the manager is initialized properly\n153: \n154: #### Scenario: 初始化失败当 clientset 为 nil\n155: - **GIVEN** a nil kubernetes clientset\n156: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with nil clientset\n157: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating kubernetes clientset is required\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: Secret 访问失败时降级到内存密钥\n160: - **GIVEN** a kubernetes clientset and permission denied error accessing Secret\n161: - **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called\n162: - **THEN** a warning is logged about the failure\n163: - **AND** RSA keys are generated in memory\n164: - **AND** the JWT manager is initialized with in-memory keys\n165: \n166: ### Requirement: JWT 认证中间件\n167: \n168: The system SHALL provide a Gin middleware that validates JWT tokens from Authorization header.\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: 中间件验证有效的令牌\n171: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT token in Authorization header as \"Bearer <token>\"\n172: - **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called with the middleware applied\n173: - **THEN** the request proceeds to the handler\n174: - **AND** the session_id claim is available in the context\n175: \n176: #### Scenario: 中间件拒绝缺少令牌的请求\n177: - **GIVEN** a request without Authorization header\n178: - **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called\n179: - **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n180: - **AND** an error response indicates missing token\n181: \n182: #### Scenario: 中间件拒绝无效的令牌\n183: - **GIVEN** a request with invalid JWT token in Authorization header\n184: - **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called\n185: - **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n186: - **AND** an error response indicates invalid token\n187: \n188: #### Scenario: 中间件拒绝过期令牌\n189: - **GIVEN** a request with expired JWT token\n190: - **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called\n191: - **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n192: - **AND** an error response indicates token expired\n193: \n194: ### Requirement: 令牌传输格式\n195: \n196: The system SHALL use standard Authorization header with Bearer scheme for token transmission.\n197: \n198: #### Scenario: 客户端使用 Bearer scheme 发送令牌\n199: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT token\n200: - **WHEN** a client sends a request to protected endpoint\n201: - **THEN** the Authorization header is set to \"Bearer <token>\"\n202: \n203: #### Scenario: 中间件从 Authorization 头提取令牌\n204: - **GIVEN** a request with Authorization header \"Bearer eyJhbGci...\"\n205: - **WHEN** the middleware processes the request\n206: - **THEN** the token \"eyJhbGci...\" is extracted from the header\n207: \n208: #### Scenario: 中间件处理非 Bearer scheme\n209: - **GIVEN** a request with Authorization header using invalid scheme\n210: - **WHEN** the middleware processes the request\n211: - **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n212: \n213: ### Requirement: 会话创建时返回令牌\n214: \n215: The system SHALL generate and return a JWT token when a new session is created.\n216: \n217: #### Scenario: 创建会话返回 JWT 令牌\n218: - **GIVEN** a request to create a new session\n219: - **WHEN** the session is successfully created\n220: - **THEN** a JWT token is generated for the session\n221: - **AND** the token is included in the response\n222: - **AND** the session_id in the token matches the created session\n223: \n224: #### Scenario: 响应包含令牌和会话信息\n225: - **GIVEN** a successfully created session\n226: - **WHEN** the response is serialized\n227: - **THEN** the response contains sessionId, sandboxId, sandboxName, and token fields\n228: - **AND** the token is a valid JWT that can be verified\n229: \n230: ### Requirement: 错误处理和日志记录\n231: \n232: The system SHALL log key events and provide structured error responses without exposing sensitive information.\n233: \n234: #### Scenario: 记录密钥生成事件\n235: - **GIVEN** a new RSA key pair is generated\n236: - **WHEN** the keys are stored in Secret\n237: - **THEN** a log entry indicates successful Secret creation\n238: - **AND** the log does not expose the private key\n239: \n240: #### Scenario: 记录密钥加载事件\n241: - **GIVEN** existing keys are loaded from Secret\n242: - **WHEN** loadKeysFromSecret succeeds\n243: - **THEN** a log entry indicates successful key loading\n244: - **AND** the log includes the Secret name\n245: \n246: #### Scenario: 记录认证失败事件\n247: - **GIVEN** a request with invalid JWT token\n248: - **WHEN** the middleware rejects the request\n249: - **THEN** a warning log entry is created\n250: - **AND** the log includes the correlation ID\n251: - **AND** the log does not include the full token\n252: \n253: #### Scenario: 返回结构化错误响应\n254: - **GIVEN** a JWT validation error occurs\n255: - **WHEN** an error response is generated\n256: - **THEN** the response includes error message and error code\n257: - **AND** the message does not expose internal details\n258: \n259: ### Requirement: 令牌过期时间配置\n260: \n261: The system SHALL use a configurable token expiration time with default of 5 minutes.\n262: \n263: #### Scenario: 默认令牌过期时间为 5 分钟\n264: - **GIVEN** a token is generated with default configuration\n265: - **WHEN** the token is examined\n266: - **THEN** the ExpiresAt claim is set to IssuedAt plus 5 minutes\n267: \n268: #### Scenario: 配置的过期时间生效\n269: - **GIVEN** a custom token expiration time is configured\n270: - **WHEN** a token is generated\n271: - **THEN** the ExpiresAt claim is set to IssuedAt plus the configured time\n272: \n273: ### Requirement: 密钥加密和 PEM 编码\n274: \n275: The system SHALL encode RSA keys in PEM format with correct block types.\n276: \n277: #### Scenario: 私钥使用 PKCS1 编码\n278: - **GIVEN** an RSA private key\n279: - **WHEN** encodeToPEM is called\n280: - **THEN** the PEM block has type \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"\n281: - **AND** the key is encoded using PKCS1 format\n282: \n283: #### Scenario: 公钥使用 PKIX 编码\n284: - **GIVEN** an RSA public key\n285: - **WHEN** encodeToPEM is called\n286: - **THEN** the PEM block has type \"PUBLIC KEY\"\n287: - **AND** the key is encoded using PKIX format\n288: \n289: #### Scenario: 解码时验证 PEM 类型\n290: - **GIVEN** a PEM-encoded block\n291: - **WHEN** parsePrivateKeyPEM is called\n292: - **THEN** the function verifies the block type is \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"\n293: - **AND** rejects blocks with incorrect type\n294: \n295: #### Scenario: 解码时验证公钥类型\n296: - **GIVEN** a PEM-encoded block\n297: - **WHEN** parsePublicKeyPEM is called\n298: - **THEN** the function verifies the block type is \"PUBLIC KEY\"\n299: - **AND** rejects blocks with incorrect type\n300: \n301: ### Requirement: Secret 访问权限验证\n302: \n303: The system SHALL handle Secret access errors gracefully and provide clear error messages.\n304: \n305: #### Scenario: Secret 不存在时创建新 Secret\n306: - **GIVEN** a request for Secret that returns 404 Not Found\n307: - **WHEN** tryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret is called\n308: - **THEN** a new Secret is created with generated keys\n309: - **AND** no error is returned\n310: \n311: #### Scenario: Secret 权限被拒绝时降级\n312: - **GIVEN** a request for Secret that returns 403 Forbidden\n313: - **WHEN** tryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret is called\n314: - **THEN** an error is logged\n315: - **AND** in-memory keys are generated as fallback\n316: \n317: #### Scenario: Secret API 错误时处理\n318: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes API error accessing Secret\n319: - **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n320: - **THEN** the error is wrapped with context\n321: - **AND** a clear error message is returned\n322: \n323: ### Requirement: JWT 声明结构\n324: \n325: The system SHALL use standard JWT claims with custom session_id field.\n326: \n327: #### Scenario: 声明包含会话 ID\n328: - **GIVEN** a JWTClaims struct\n329: - **WHEN** the struct is populated with session ID\n330: - **THEN** the SessionID field is set to the provided value\n331: - **AND** the field is JSON-encoded as \"session_id\"\n332: \n333: #### Scenario: 声明包含标准 RegisteredClaims\n334: - **GIVEN** a JWTClaims struct\n335: - **WHEN** the struct is used for token generation\n336: - **THEN** the token includes standard claims: Issuer, Subject, Audience, ExpiresAt, IssuedAt, NotBefore, ID\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: 声明支持 JSON 序列化\n339: - **GIVEN** a JWTClaims struct with populated fields\n340: - **WHEN** the struct is serialized to JSON\n341: - **THEN** all fields are correctly encoded in camelCase\n342: - **AND** the JSON is valid and can be deserialized\n343: \n344: ### Requirement: 并发安全\n345: \n346: The system SHALL support concurrent token generation and validation operations.\n347: \n348: #### Scenario: 并发生成多个令牌\n349: - **GIVEN** multiple goroutines calling GenerateToken simultaneously\n350: - **WHEN** the tokens are generated\n351: - **THEN** all tokens are successfully generated\n352: - **AND** each token has a unique session_id\n353: - **AND** no race conditions occur\n354: \n355: #### Scenario: 并发验证多个令牌\n356: - **GIVEN** multiple goroutines calling ValidateToken simultaneously\n357: - **WHEN** the tokens are validated\n358: - **THEN** all validations are performed correctly\n359: - **AND** no race conditions occur\n360: \n361: ### Requirement: 令牌签名算法验证\n362: \n363: The system SHALL verify the signing algorithm used in tokens to prevent algorithm confusion attacks.\n364: \n365: #### Scenario: 拒绝非 RSA 签名算法\n366: - **GIVEN** a JWT token signed with HS256 (HMAC) algorithm\n367: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n368: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating unexpected signing method\n369: \n370: #### Scenario: 验证 RS256 签名算法\n371: - **GIVEN** a JWT token signed with RS256 algorithm\n372: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n373: - **THEN** the signature is verified using RSA public key\n374: - **AND** the token is accepted if valid\n375: \n376: #### Scenario: 检测算法头篡改\n377: - **GIVEN** a JWT token with \"alg\" header modified to \"none\"\n378: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n379: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating unexpected signing method\n380: \n381: ### Requirement: 令牌过期验证\n382: \n383: The system SHALL reject tokens that have passed their expiration time.\n384: \n385: #### Scenario: 拒绝刚刚过期的令牌\n386: - **GIVEN** a token that expired 1 second ago\n387: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n388: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token has expired\n389: \n390: #### Scenario: 接受未过期的令牌\n391: - **GIVEN** a token that expires in the future\n392: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n393: - **THEN** the token is validated successfully\n394: - **AND** the claims are returned\n395: \n396: #### Scenario: NotBefore 验证\n397: - **GIVEN** a token with NotBefore set to future time\n398: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called before NotBefore time\n399: - **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token is not yet valid\n400: \n401: ### Requirement: 命名空间隔离\n402: \n403: The system SHALL use the configured namespace for Secret operations.\n404: \n405: #### Scenario: 使用指定命名空间访问 Secret\n406: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager configured with namespace \"production\"\n407: - **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n408: - **THEN** the Secret is accessed in the \"production\" namespace\n409: - **AND** operations do not affect other namespaces\n410: \n411: #### Scenario: 使用默认命名空间\n412: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized without namespace\n413: - **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n414: - **THEN** the default namespace (\"agentcube\") is used\n415: - **AND** Secret is accessed in the default namespace\n416: \n417: ### Requirement: Secret 命名约定\n418: \n419: The system SHALL use a consistent Secret name for key storage.\n420: \n421: #### Scenario: Secret 名称固定为 \"agentcube-jwt-keys\"\n422: - **GIVEN** any JWT manager instance\n423: - **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n424: - **THEN** the Secret name is always \"agentcube-jwt-keys\"\n425: - **AND** the Secret is stored and retrieved using this name\n426: \n427: ### Requirement: JWT 管理器不可变密钥\n428: \n429: The system SHALL not allow key regeneration after initialization.\n430: \n431: #### Scenario: 初始化后密钥保持不变\n432: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized with keys\n433: - **WHEN** multiple calls to GenerateToken are made\n434: - **THEN** all tokens are signed with the same private key\n435: - **AND** all tokens can be verified with the same public key\n436: \n437: #### Scenario: 重启后密钥从 Secret 加载\n438: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager that stored keys in Secret\n439: - **WHEN** the service is restarted and JWT manager is reinitialized\n440: - **THEN** the same keys are loaded from the Secret\n441: - **AND** previously issued tokens remain valid\n442: \n443: ### Requirement: 性能要求\n444: \n445: The system SHALL meet performance targets for token operations.\n446: \n447: #### Scenario: 令牌生成延迟\n448: - **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized with keys\n449: - **WHEN** GenerateToken is called multiple times\n450: - **THEN** the P99 latency is less than 10ms\n451: \n452: #### Scenario: 令牌验证延迟\n453: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT token\n454: - **WHEN** ValidateToken is called multiple times\n455: - **THEN** the P99 latency is less than 5ms\n456: \n457: ### Requirement: 日志级别控制\n458: \n459: The system SHALL use appropriate log levels for different events.\n460: \n461: #### Scenario: 信息日志用于正常操作\n462: - **GIVEN** successful key loading or Secret creation\n463: - **WHEN** these operations complete\n464: - **THEN** log entries use Info level\n465: - **AND** include relevant context\n466: \n467: #### Scenario: 警告日志用于降级场景\n468: - **GIVEN** Secret access failure with fallback to in-memory keys\n469: - **WHEN** the fallback occurs\n470: - **THEN** log entries use Warning level\n471: - **AND** include the original error\n472: \n473: #### Scenario: 错误日志用于失败场景\n474: - **GIVEN** critical failures like key generation errors\n475: - **WHEN** these failures occur\n476: - **THEN** log entries use Error level\n477: - **AND** include detailed error information\n478: \n479: ### Requirement: 上下文传递\n480: \n481: The system SHALL pass session information to request handlers after successful authentication.\n482: \n483: #### Scenario: 中间件设置会话 ID 到上下文\n484: - **GIVEN** a valid JWT token with session_id claim\n485: - **WHEN** the middleware successfully validates the token\n486: - **THEN** the session_id is stored in the Gin context\n487: - **AND** handlers can retrieve it from the context\n488: \n489: #### Scenario: 处理器从上下文获取会话 ID\n490: - **GIVEN** a request authenticated with JWT token\n491: - **WHEN** a handler needs the session ID\n492: - **THEN** the handler retrieves it from the Gin context\n493: - **AND** uses it for session-specific operations\n\n(End of file - total 493 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Router JWT 认证与签发 Specification\n\n## Purpose\n\n实现 Router 模块的 JWT（JSON Web Token）认证与签发功能，为 AgentCube 平台提供安全的会话认证机制。该模块负责生成、验证和管理 JWT 令牌，用于认证和授权 Router 请求，确保只有合法的会话才能访问后端服务。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: JWT 令牌生成与会话关联\n\nThe system SHALL generate a JWT token for each session using RS256 signing algorithm with the session ID included in the claims.\n\n#### Scenario: 生成包含会话 ID 的 JWT 令牌\n- **GIVEN** a valid session ID and initialized JWT manager with RSA key pair\n- **WHEN** GenerateToken is called with the session ID\n- **THEN** a JWT token is returned with session_id claim containing the provided session ID\n- **AND** the token includes standard RegisteredClaims with IssuedAt, ExpiresAt, and NotBefore timestamps\n- **AND** the token is signed using RS256 algorithm\n\n#### Scenario: 生成的令牌包含标准声明","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md","time":{"start":1775852448894,"end":1775852448909}}}}
